Product Version     25.10    Cadence Design Systems, Inc.
deleteAllCellPad(25.10)                                deleteAllCellPad(25.10)

Name
       deleteAllCellPad  - Removes placement padding specified by specifyCell-
       Pad for all cells

Syntax
       deleteAllCellPad

       Removes placement padding specified by specifyCellPad for all cells. If
       you run this command before running  checkPlace,  checkPlace  does  not
       consider the cell padding when calculating effective utilization.

Parameters
       None

Examples
       The following set of commands specifies the cell padding for HDSDFRSPQ1
       and HDSDFRSPQ2, and then deletes all padding by using deleteAllCellPad:

       specifyCellPad HDSDFRSPQ1 2

        specifyCellPad HDSDFRSPQ2 2

        deleteAllCellPad

